title: Charging | Under Armour Headphones Wireless | Engineered by JBL
description:
In this video, learn how to properly fit your UA Headphones Wireless | Engineered by JBL.

UA Headphones Wireless | Engineered by JBL are designed by athletes for athletes to set the new standard of what a sport headphone should be. Sweat proof and built to withstand any workout, they’re guaranteed to be the most comfortable headphones you’ll ever wear. They’ll never hurt, fall out, or get in your way. UA Headphones Wireless | Engineered by JBL are Bluetooth enabled freeing you from wires and distractions. Power every workout with JBL Signature Sound so you can finish strong.

transcripts: UA headphones wireless engineered by JBL connect to your phone via Bluetooth for best performance weather cord in front press and hold the middle buttons to power on once powered on the LED will flash blue to put the headphones in pairing mode begin with the headphones powered on. Next press and hold the middle button until the LED flashes red and blue be sure to activate Bluetooth on your phone and select ua JBL wireless to power off press and hold the middle button until the LED turns red this helps to conserve battery life while in use and audio prop will alert you when the battery is low LED light will also flash red to recharge plug one end of the USB charger to the inline control and the other into a USB port LED will turn solid red when charging and off when finished.
